response.original_title: The Bear Wit Project - Blair Witch Parody by the Muppets
response.overview: A very funny parody of on of the most overrated movies of the 90s, courtesy of our favourite handheld comedians from the small screen: The Muppets. Look, stare, understand... and scream! (with laughter)
